    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Project Charter: Goal: Inform -> Viz: Structured HTML/CSS table -> Justification: The clearest and most professional way to present core project parameters.
        - Key Questions: Goal: Organize/Inform -> Viz: 3-Card Layout -> Justification: Breaks down the required investigation into logical, digestible themes (Process, Technology, Data).
        - Action Plan: Goal: Organize/Change -> Viz: Structured HTML/CSS Timeline -> Justification: The most intuitive way to present a time-based, phased plan, making it feel concrete and manageable.
        - Deliverables & Success Metrics: Goal: Inform -> Viz: Two-column list layout -> Justification: Clearly separates the outputs (what we will create) from the outcomes (how we will measure success).
    -->
